1) Now reason for true literal l is no more composed by all false literals of l but just the false ones greater than the second max undefined
2) The non-shared part of the reason is calculated: [lit for lit in g.ord_l[i::j] if propagator.I[lit] == False], before update it was up to i::
3) First the way of propagation with EO was: starting from the lowest try to propagate. 
    Now it first tries to propagate the max undefined, if it is not propagate the 
    propagation for false literal can take place
4) propagation of falses:
    Before:
    for l in g.ord_l:
            if I[l] is None:
                if mps - mw_g + weight[l] < lb:
                    # infer l as false
                    S.append(not_(l))
                    g.decrease_und()
                else:
                    break
    After:
    start = g.max_und if not g.max_und is None else 0
    for i in range(start-1,-1,-1):
        l = g.ord_l[i]
        if propagator.I[l] is None:
            if propagator.mps(g, l, assumed=True) < propagator.lb:
                S.extend([not_(lit) for lit in g.ord_l[i::-1] if propagator.I[lit] is None])
                break

